00:21:20,660 --> 00:21:25,810
♫Ever since I met you,
I've known that our love is true♫

332
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:32,120
♫I used to feel the void,♫

333
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:36,410
♫But you came to brighten my days♫

334
00:21:36,450 --> 00:21:41,150
