380
00:27:33,430 --> 00:27:34,800
How was that pointless, Mom?

381
00:27:35,290 --> 00:27:37,620
Singing a song in that kind of bar.

382
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,870
Where we put ourselves

383
