- Our pleasure.

484
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,660
They'll have good fortune
after getting it done.

485
00:35:28,690 --> 00:35:30,060
It helps us feel better.

486
00:35:30,720 --> 00:35:32,850
A-ping, walk the guests out, please.

487
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:33,840
- See you next time.
- See you.

488
00:35:33,870 --> 00:35:35,000
- Thank you so much.
- Goodbye.

489
00:35:35,020 --> 00:35:36,200
Get there safely.

490
00:35:36,230 --> 00:35:37,630
See you next time. See you.

491
00:35:37,660 --> 00:35:39,850
Their house is huge.
I want to come here more often.

492
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,880
- That sounds great.
- Yeah.

493
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:44,160
What a relieved feeling.

494
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:45,280
Yeah, that's great.

495
00:35:45,830 --> 00:35:47,980
- Oh, they're here!
- You came back at the right time.

496
00:35:48,210 --> 00:35:51,320
Hey, that's great. Perfect timing.

497
00:35:51,710 --> 00:35:53,670
I had feng shui masters

498
00:35:53,690 --> 00:35:55,280
prepare water for you two to bathe.

499
00:35:55,420 --> 00:35:56,710
It's holy water

500
00:35:56,740 --> 00:35:58,610
that's already been blessed.

501
00:35:58,690 --> 00:36:02,030
After a tiring day, you should take
a bath to feel refreshed, okay?

502
00:36:02,270 --> 00:36:02,870
Yeah.

503
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:05,630
And what about me?
Is there any left for me?

504
00:36:06,520 --> 00:36:08,950
Just stick to your usual water.

505
00:36:09,450 --> 00:36:10,990
Hey, what? Why?!

506
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:14,290
I want to be unlucky, too.

507
00:36:14,330 --> 00:36:15,980
Look, he's got so many things.

508
00:36:16,110 --> 00:36:17,880
You're just talking nonsense.

509
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:20,760
Go, go, Itthi and Ritt.
Go take a bath to feel refreshed.

510
00:36:20,790 --> 00:36:21,710
- Go, go, go.
- Go, go, go.

511
00:36:21,750 --> 00:36:23,850
Take a long bath, okay? Go, go.

512
00:36:24,650 --> 00:36:26,010
We've already prepared it for you.

513
00:36:26,890 --> 00:36:30,160
Just soak in the tub, you know?
Wash away the negativity.

514
00:36:30,890 --> 00:36:31,600
Okay, Grandma.

515
00:36:36,540 --> 00:36:38,120
Do you think it is too warm?

516
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:40,020
Yeah.

517
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:43,300
This is like a tom yum pot

518
00:36:44,410 --> 00:36:45,990
but without lemongrass
and kaffir lime leaves.

519
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:48,860
If Grandma hears that,

520
00:36:49,310 --> 00:36:50,540
she will be very sad.

521
00:36:51,390 --> 00:36:52,150
I heard...

522
00:36:52,170 --> 00:36:54,740
she had feng shui masters
preparing this all afternoon.

523
00:36:55,030 --> 00:36:55,710
But...

524
00:36:55,990 --> 00:36:58,010
why do we have to bathe
in this kind of water?

525
00:36:58,910 --> 00:36:59,980
Chinese people

526
00:37:00,310 --> 00:37:01,510
believe that...

527
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:03,040
flowers

528
00:37:03,470 --> 00:37:04,900
can drive away bad luck.

529
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:07,000
Lanna people believe that...

530
00:37:07,450 --> 00:37:10,000
the smell of herbs
can help ease severe misfortune.

531
00:37:10,330 --> 00:37:12,780
But the Romani call this...

532
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:14,230
a cleansing bath.

533
00:37:14,980 --> 00:37:16,220
If we bathe in it,
we will have good fortune.

534
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:18,560
This chrysanthemum flower

535
00:37:18,970 --> 00:37:19,890
will help you live longer

536
00:37:20,380 --> 00:37:21,520
and be healthy.

537
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:24,020
The yellow

538
00:37:24,530 --> 00:37:26,840
can also wash away the misery
and enhance good fortune.

539
00:37:27,330 --> 00:37:28,380
For the bamboo leaf...

540
00:37:29,150 --> 00:37:31,640
it helps us become
as strong as its stalk,

541
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:33,310
and it also helps ward off

542
00:37:33,330 --> 00:37:35,440
misfortune from our bodies.

543
00:37:36,090 --> 00:37:36,900
Jasmine

544
00:37:37,640 --> 00:37:39,410
is used in a life extension ceremony.

545
00:37:40,710 --> 00:37:42,210
It means a new beginning.

546
00:37:43,290 --> 00:37:44,420
For orange peel,

547
00:37:45,290 --> 00:37:46,290
it means good luck.

548
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,940
Its smell also helps relieve stress.

549
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:51,550
Wild betel and ngai camphor leaves

550
00:37:52,830 --> 00:37:54,920
help ward off evil spirits.

551
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:57,710
And the essential oil helps kill germs.

552
00:37:58,300 --> 00:37:59,520
You know a lot about it.

553
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:01,520
And...

554
00:38:02,370 --> 00:38:03,770
what if we go by science?

555
00:38:04,660 --> 00:38:06,610
It is probably aromatherapy.

556
00:38:07,970 --> 00:38:10,180
Try taking a deep breath.

557
00:38:10,430 --> 00:38:11,430
It makes us feel refreshed

558
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:15,240
because these leaves and flowers

559
00:38:15,560 --> 00:38:17,220
mix with the water,

560
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,650
then act on our skin.

561
00:38:19,150 --> 00:38:22,710
But the other beliefs
might be encouragement

562
00:38:23,850 --> 00:38:24,980
to make us feel like...

563
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:27,170
we're washing away
all negativity with this water.

564
00:38:27,790 --> 00:38:28,790
Whoa,

565
00:38:29,590 --> 00:38:31,580
you know both beliefs

566
00:38:32,250 --> 00:38:33,770
and science,

567
00:38:33,930 --> 00:38:35,100
all the aspects.

568
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:37,180
I think...

569
00:38:37,540 --> 00:38:41,130
I should ask you for help
with my thesis research.

570
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:42,600
Sure, anytime.

571
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:45,150
I can help you

572
00:38:46,090 --> 00:38:47,530
with everything you want.

573
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:50,210
You're the cutest one.

574
00:38:52,290 --> 00:38:53,200
So cute

575
00:38:55,730 --> 00:38:56,730
that it's scary.

576
00:38:58,850 --> 00:38:59,960
What makes you scared?

577
00:39:01,590 --> 00:39:02,260
Well...

578
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:03,600
I'm afraid that...

579
00:39:05,250 --> 00:39:06,840
if one day,

580
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:09,170
I'm not the person you thought I was,

581
00:39:10,770 --> 00:39:13,220
- will you...
- I don't want you to be anything else.

582
00:39:14,350 --> 00:39:15,670
It is best that

583
00:39:15,690 --> 00:39:17,130
you are who you are.

584
00:39:18,370 --> 00:39:19,310
Do you understand that?

585
00:39:21,550 --> 00:39:22,450
You tiny one.

586
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:25,100
You scaredy cat.

587
00:39:26,150 --> 00:39:27,360
You're so paranoid.

588
00:39:48,310 --> 00:39:49,370
Can you scrub my back?

589
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,150
Well...

590
00:39:52,020 --> 00:39:53,020
You're coaxing, right?

591
00:39:53,510 --> 00:39:54,420
I know you.

592
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,320
Scrub my back hard, please.

593
00:40:03,690 --> 00:40:05,370
- Hard?
- Yeah.

594
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,930
Actually, it can be harder,

595
00:40:14,030 --> 00:40:15,620
but I'm afraid you'll be hurt.

596
00:40:17,040 --> 00:40:18,040
Try it.

597
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:28,210
Come on.

598
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:30,270
It's my turn.

599
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:32,920
Turn around.

600
00:40:48,200 --> 00:40:49,360
Do you enjoy it?

601
00:40:55,750 --> 00:40:58,810
If you do, I'll tell Grandma
to prepare this for us more often.

602
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:21,920
How can you come here?

603
00:43:22,320 --> 00:43:23,430
Don't you need to look after the bar?

604
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:24,690
How is your mother?

605
00:43:27,010 --> 00:43:28,380
The doctor hasn't come out yet.

606
00:43:29,640 --> 00:43:30,600
Don't worry.

607
00:43:31,130 --> 00:43:32,230
She's under the doctor's care now.

608
00:43:40,320 --> 00:43:41,440
How was she, doctor?

609
00:43:41,680 --> 00:43:44,570
Your mother isn't seriously injured.
There is just a little bruise.

610
00:43:44,730 --> 00:43:48,320
Make sure she takes medication
and does physical therapy consistently

611
00:43:48,670 --> 00:43:50,490
in order to keep her condition stable.

612
00:43:51,270 --> 00:43:52,290
I have to go now.

613
00:43:53,260 --> 00:43:54,920
- Thank you, doctor.
- Thank you so much.

614
00:43:57,390 --> 00:43:58,190
Mom.

615
00:44:02,020 --> 00:44:03,120
How do you feel now?

616
00:44:03,450 --> 00:44:04,860
A little painful.

617
00:44:04,960 --> 00:44:06,200
Your legs are fine, right?

618
00:44:10,210 --> 00:44:11,550
Let's go home together then.

619
00:44:46,260 --> 00:44:47,290
Thank you so much

620
00:44:47,380 --> 00:44:49,030
for taking Pitcha and me here.

621
00:44:49,610 --> 00:44:50,610
It's my pleasure.

622
00:44:50,910 --> 00:44:54,260
Please take care of yourself
so that you'll get healthy again soon.

623
00:44:54,730 --> 00:44:55,730
Thank you so much.

624
00:44:57,500 --> 00:44:59,980
Let me get my mom to bed first.

625
00:45:00,160 --> 00:45:00,910
Wait a minute.

626
00:45:02,180 --> 00:45:03,030
Let's go, Mom.

627
00:45:05,330 --> 00:45:06,130
Be careful.

628
00:45:36,060 --> 00:45:38,040
Are you and your mom close?

629
00:45:39,100 --> 00:45:40,100
What do you think?

630
00:45:41,380 --> 00:45:42,620
A single mom

631
00:45:42,910 --> 00:45:43,910
and her one and only son.

632
00:45:47,090 --> 00:45:49,400
My mom is really strict, you know?

633
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:52,030
If she knows that you are the bar owner,

634
00:45:52,470 --> 00:45:53,970
she might ask me
to stop seeing you.

635
00:45:55,060 --> 00:45:56,060
Why?

636
00:45:57,430 --> 00:45:59,220
She considers it something bad.

637
00:46:02,580 --> 00:46:04,410
My life before moving to Korea

638
00:46:04,810 --> 00:46:06,800
has always been under her rules,

639
00:46:07,860 --> 00:46:10,800
so I rarely had friends
or had fun with them.

640
00:46:11,050 --> 00:46:11,830
My mom

641
00:46:11,850 --> 00:46:14,050
has always wanted me to be an artist.

642
00:46:15,400 --> 00:46:16,880
She used to be a dancesport athlete

643
00:46:17,590 --> 00:46:18,780
at the national level,

644
00:46:20,150 --> 00:46:22,180
but she has muscle weakness,

645
00:46:22,720 --> 00:46:25,120
which closed the door
to her dancesport career.

646
00:46:26,640 --> 00:46:29,890
I became the hope
to make her dream come true.

647
00:46:32,750 --> 00:46:33,840
So it means that you...

648
00:46:34,420 --> 00:46:36,090
used to do dancesport, right?

649
00:46:37,410 --> 00:46:38,000
Yeah.

650
00:46:38,850 --> 00:46:39,770
When I was younger.

651
00:46:40,610 --> 00:46:41,800
But when I grew up,

652
00:46:42,410 --> 00:46:43,410
she saw that

653
00:46:43,760 --> 00:46:45,520
being a Korean idol might be better,

654
00:46:45,880 --> 00:46:47,080
so she told me to take this path.

655
00:46:51,100 --> 00:46:53,100
And...do you like it?

656
00:47:02,100 --> 00:47:03,520
It's my mom's dream.

657
00:47:05,130 --> 00:47:06,130
I love her.

658
00:47:06,950 --> 00:47:08,410
I just want to make her happy.

659
00:47:10,800 --> 00:47:12,130
But what about your dream?

660
00:47:13,450 --> 00:47:15,800
Is your dream like her dream?

661
00:47:24,120 --> 00:47:27,490
♫I used to feel the void,♫

662
00:47:27,520 --> 00:47:31,790
♫But you came to brighten my days♫

663
00:47:31,830 --> 00:47:37,070
♫You made me realize♫

664
00:47:39,560 --> 00:47:43,070
♫What true love is like♫

665
00:47:43,100 --> 00:47:46,340
♫When you came into my heart,♫

666
00:47:46,370 --> 00:47:49,490
♫You completely changed♫

667
00:47:49,530 --> 00:47:53,260
♫The world I'd known♫

668
00:47:53,290 --> 00:47:57,100
♫I don't know when these feelings started♫

669
00:47:57,140 --> 00:48:00,460
♫I love you with all my heart♫

670
00:48:01,440 --> 00:48:02,530
It is tiring

671
00:48:03,810 --> 00:48:05,420
to carry all the expectations, right?

672
00:48:07,490 --> 00:48:09,120
Every time she hugs me,

673
00:48:09,560 --> 00:48:11,550
I feel like she has passed her dream

674
00:48:11,570 --> 00:48:13,700
on to me to pursue for her,

675
00:48:14,990 --> 00:48:17,430
so much so that
I'm not sure what I really want to do.

676
00:48:20,100 --> 00:48:21,060
You see?

677
00:48:21,570 --> 00:48:22,840
I'm hugging you.

678
00:48:23,500 --> 00:48:24,680
You can be anything

679
00:48:24,820 --> 00:48:26,800
or whoever you want to be in my arms.

680
00:48:28,730 --> 00:48:31,080
You can place everything
you've been carrying.

681
00:48:31,260 --> 00:48:32,260
Leave it for now.

682
00:48:32,580 --> 00:48:33,580
Leave it on me, okay?

683
00:48:35,440 --> 00:48:36,900
Try imagining that

684
00:48:37,310 --> 00:48:38,810
you are here with me.

685
00:48:39,340 --> 00:48:40,780
There has never been even
a competition stage.

686
00:48:41,270 --> 00:48:43,300
The competition has never happened.

687
00:48:43,690 --> 00:48:45,580
No one's expectations have been put on you.

688
00:48:46,900 --> 00:48:47,900
It's just you

689
00:48:48,600 --> 00:48:49,600
and yourself,

690
00:48:50,900 --> 00:48:53,330
and all of the real feelings inside you.

691
00:48:57,420 --> 00:48:59,680
Try listening to your heart.

692
00:49:01,450 --> 00:49:02,680
What is it telling you...

693
00:49:02,990 --> 00:49:04,710
to do now?

694
00:49:13,300 --> 00:49:14,500
Try listening to...

695
00:49:15,390 --> 00:49:16,670
what it is telling you

696
00:49:17,240 --> 00:49:18,420
to do now.

697
00:49:36,040 --> 00:49:37,170
It's telling me that...

698
00:49:39,230 --> 00:49:40,480
I want to do this.

699
00:53:16,880 --> 00:53:18,380
[Unknown number:

700
00:53:18,410 --> 00:53:21,520
If you don't want the truth
to come out, call back before noon]

701
00:53:31,600 --> 00:53:32,830
I'm sorry.

702
00:53:32,910 --> 00:53:34,210
I didn't mean to.

703
00:53:34,250 --> 00:53:35,710
I'm so sorry.

704
00:53:36,280 --> 00:53:37,620
Please don't push me away.

705
00:53:42,360 --> 00:53:43,360
[There is only one truth,
just as there is one true identity]

706
00:53:46,480 --> 00:53:47,840
What if one day...

707
00:53:49,330 --> 00:53:50,530
I did something bad?

708
00:53:52,360 --> 00:53:54,790
If I let you down or hurt your feelings,

709
00:53:57,180 --> 00:53:58,930
would you still hold me like this?

710
00:54:16,290 --> 00:54:21,430
♫I never knew that one day I could feel♫

711
00:54:22,840 --> 00:54:27,680
♫For someone so wholeheartedly♫

712
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:35,270
♫With you beside me,
I can feel like myself♫

713
00:54:35,530 --> 00:54:40,810
♫The darkness I felt
disappeared after we met♫

714
00:54:43,640 --> 00:54:46,990
♫I used to feel the void,♫

715
00:54:47,040 --> 00:54:51,270
♫But you came to brighten my days♫

716
00:54:51,320 --> 00:54:55,940
♫You made me realize♫

717
00:54:55,990 --> 00:54:59,490
♫What true love is like♫

718
00:54:59,520 --> 00:55:02,720
♫When you came into my heart,♫

719
00:55:02,830 --> 00:55:05,790
♫You completely changed♫

720
00:55:05,810 --> 00:55:09,720
♫The world I'd known♫

721
00:55:09,770 --> 00:55:13,490
♫I don't know when these feelings started♫

722
00:55:13,510 --> 00:55:16,580
♫I love you with all my heart♫

723
00:55:17,600 --> 00:55:20,830
♫I just want to let you know♫

724
00:55:20,890 --> 00:55:27,510
♫With love for only you,
my heart overflows♫
